=== KPI Widget ===

==== Functionality ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.KPIWidget
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}

==== Configuration Settings ====

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.widget.KPIWidget
| type = CONFIGURATION
}}

==== Examples ====
* Example with static values:
<source>
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.KPIWidget | 
 styling = 
   {{ cssClass = 'eventSummary'
   }}
 | kpi = {{ 
      {{ cssClass = 'error'
       | resource = 'MyEventPage'
       | description = 'Errors'
       | label = 'Error'
       | params = {{ 
            {{ name = 'type'
             | value = 'ERROR'
            }} }}
       | value = '100'
      }} | 
      {{ cssClass = 'warning'
       | description = 'Warnings'
       | label = 'Warning'
       | value = '1'
      }} | 
      {{ cssClass = 'info'
       | description = 'Infos'
       | label = 'Info'
       | value = '1'
      }} }}
}}
</source>

The result looks like this:
<img src="../images/help/KPIWidget/exampleKPI.png" alt="IMAGE:Example result"/>

* Example with query values:
<source>
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.KPIWidget | 
 styling = 
   {{ cssClass = 'eventSummary'
   }}
 | kpi = {{ 
      {{ cssClass = 'error'
       | resource = 'EventDetailPage'
       | description = 'Errors'
       | label = 'Error'
       | params = {{ 
            {{ name = 'type'
             | value = 'ERROR'
            }} }}
       | value = $SELECT (COUNT(?event) AS ?cnt) WHERE { ?event event:eventSource ?? . ?event event:classification "ERROR" }$
      }} | 
      {{ cssClass = 'warning'
       | description = 'Warnings'
       | label = 'Warning'
       | value = $SELECT (COUNT(?event) AS ?cnt) WHERE { ?event event:eventSource ?? . ?event event:classification "WARNING" }$
      }} | 
      {{ cssClass = 'info'
       | description = 'Infos'
       | label = 'Info'
       | value = $SELECT (COUNT(?event) AS ?cnt) WHERE { ?event event:eventSource ?? . ?event event:classification "INFORMATION" }$
      }} }}
}}
</source>